To draw a chessboard with a given FEN (Forsyth-Edwards Notation) in LaTeX, you can use the `chessboard` package. It requires the `tikz` package, which is necessary for drawing diagrams. First, add the following packages in the preamble of your LaTeX document:
```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{chessboard}
\usepackage{tikz}
% The rest of your document content
```
Now, you can use the following code to create a chessboard with a given FEN notation. You need to replace the placeholders `[fen]` with your actual FEN notation.
```less
